		category: "Culture",
		readTime: "5 min read",
		date: "February 2026",
		icon: "/assets/design-assets/noun-losar-celebration-6090511.svg"
	},
	{
		slug: "express-desires-needs-abilities-tibetan",
		title: "How to Express Desires, Needs, and Abilities in Tibetan",
		excerpt: "Ever wished you could say \"I want to go to Tibet\" or \"She knows how to write in Tibetan\"? Explore modal verbs in Tibetan and learn to express wants, needs, abilities, and experiences.",
