		readTime: "5 min read",
		date: "February 2026",
		icon: "/assets/design-assets/noun-wish-6629758.svg"
	},
	{
		slug: "white-wednesday-lhag-kar",
		title: "How to Celebrate Lhag-kar: The Significance of \"White Wednesday\" in Tibetan Culture",
		excerpt: "If you have spent any time in Tibetan communities, you may have noticed that on Wednesdays, the streets bloom with the beautiful colors of traditional Chupas. Discover the meaning of Lhag-kar and how you can participate.",
