		readTime: "5 min read",
		date: "February 2026",
		icon: "/assets/design-assets/noun-incense-8229125.svg"
	},
	{
		slug: "classical-vs-colloquial-tibetan",
		title: "Classical vs Colloquial Tibetan: Which Should You Learn?",
